API Notes 3

Data Persistence:

	1. Client Side - Storing directly on your computer(local browser)
		- local storage
		- session storage
		- cookies
		- cache storage

	2. Server Side - on a server, in a data base


	Look up:
		localstorage.clear()
		localStorage.setItem()
		localStorage.getItem()

		all browsers use cookies, not all browsers use localStorage or sessionStorage

		You can also set expiration date on cookies

		JSON.stringify() - converts object to a string

		JSON.parse() - converts string to an object

		